sighttpd - A stream ingress HTTP server
=======================================

sighttpd is an HTTP server designed to work with realtime stream input.
It is particularly useful for making streams from a camera available to multiple
clients.

Installation
------------

This source archive uses the GNU autotools to build. Ensure that the standard GNU
build environment is available, including autoconf, automake, pkg-config.

To build:

    autoreconf -vif
    ./configure
    make
    make install

